column16: Max Kepler pops out to first baseman C.  J.   Cron in foul territory.
Byung Ho Park grounds out softly, catcher Jett Bandy to first baseman C.   Cron.   Brian Dozier to 2nd.
Byron Buxton grounds into a force out, shortstop Gregorio Petit to second baseman Johnny Giavotella.   Kurt Suzuki out at 2nd.
Kurt Suzuki singles on a fly ball to right fielder Kole Calhoun.   Brian Dozier scores.    Max Kepler to 3rd.
Max Kepler grounds into a force out, third baseman Yunel Escobar to second baseman Johnny Giavotella.   Joe Mauer scores.    Brian Dozier to 3rd.    Byung Ho Park out at 2nd.    Max Kepler to 1st.
Byung Ho Park reaches on a force attempt, fielding error by shortstop Gregorio Petit.   Joe Mauer to 3rd.    Brian Dozier to 2nd.
Trevor Plouffe grounds out softly, catcher Carlos Perez to first baseman Albert Pujols.   Joe Mauer to 2nd.
Joe Mauer reaches on a fielding error by shortstop Gregorio Petit.
Robbie Grossman homers (5) on a fly ball to center field.
